#### 3. Componente Global de Tema

**Estructura Recomendada:**

```
constants/
  ├── theme.ts (Actualizar: agregar Light theme)
  └── colors.ts (Opcional: separar colores por modo)

hooks/
  ├── use-color-scheme.ts (EXISTENTE - mejorar)
  └── use-theme.ts (NUEVO - contexto global de tema)

context/
  └── ThemeContext.tsx (NUEVO - proveedor de tema)
```

**ThemeContext.tsx (Pseudocódigo):**

```typescript
import React, { createContext, useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import { useColorScheme } from 'react-native';
import AsyncStorage from '@react-native-async-storage/async-storage';

export const ThemeContext = createContext();

export const ThemeProvider = ({ children }) => {
  const systemScheme = useColorScheme();
  const [theme, setTheme] = useState(systemScheme || 'dark');

  useEffect(() => {
    // Cargar preferencia guardada
    const loadTheme = async () => {
      const saved = await AsyncStorage.getItem('app-theme');
      if (saved) setTheme(saved);
    };
    loadTheme();
  }, []);

  const toggleTheme = async () => {
    const newTheme = theme === 'dark' ? 'light' : 'dark';
    setTheme(newTheme);
    await AsyncStorage.setItem('app-theme', newTheme);
  };

  const colors = theme === 'dark' ? DARK_COLORS : LIGHT_COLORS;

  return (
    <ThemeContext.Provider value={{ theme, toggleTheme, colors }}>
      {children}
    </ThemeContext.Provider>
  );
};
```

